  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age: 21-46 years, 63-81 years old

          -  Not diagnosed with diabetes or metabolic syndrome

          -  Clinically normal blood laboratory values

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age: 21 years of younger, 47-62 years old, and 82 years and older

          -  BMI: 20-29 kg/m

          -  Weight stable: &lt;2kg change within the last 3 months

          -  Physical Activity: constant habitual pattern, no deviation &gt;1x week of 30/minute
             sessions within the last 3 months

        Clinically abnormal values:

          -  Blood

          -  Urine

        Also, exclude any:

          -  Using meds that would influence appetite

          -  Using any anti-inflammatory steroid medications

          -  Has a joint replacement

          -  A medical condition that might place them at risk for participating in the study or
             interfere with successful completion of the study
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
